author: Home RenoVision DIY
description: We tested four of the most popular toilets from Home Depot and Lowe’s, ranging from $99 to $499, to find out which one actually performs best. From flush power and golf ball tests to bowl cleaning and spray coverage, we put each toilet through real-world challenges. If you’re shopping for a new toilet, this toilet comparison and flush test will show you which one is truly worth your money. If you found this video helpful, please subscribe. Hope you enjoy. Cheers!
title: The Toilet Showdown You Didn’t Know You Needed
